See More ( Title ) Management Services Director Email

Email Terri Toledo

Department: City Manager

Terri Toledo is Director of Management Services and oversees the departments of People and Culture, Pflugerville Animal Welfare Services and Information Technology. She has worked for the City of Pflugerville for more than 16 years serving previously as Communications Director and Public Information Officer. In those roles she worked on Pflugerville's communications messages, strategy and outreach. Prior to the City of Pflugerville, Toledo worked for the City of Round Rock.
